@startuml
title Generator Runtime (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FCFCFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #5D4037
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B3E5FC
component "athena-js CLI" as Cli #FFE082
component "dist/cli/index.js" as MissingCli #EF9A9A
component "Schema Introspection" as Introspection #FFF59D
component "Typed Registry APIs" as Registry #C5E1A5

Consumer --> Cli : "athena-js generate"
Cli --> MissingCli : dynamic import
MissingCli ..> Cli : runtime missing
Registry ..> Introspection : manual usage only

note right of Cli
No first-class generator config file.
No artifact emission pipeline.
Provider adapters not wired.
end note
@enduml
